    "Local Hardhat validation deploys MockUSDC automatically because TavernEscrow reads token decimals in the constructor.",
    "TavernStaking was deployed to Base Sepolia at 0x50a8866F7E24441e636aFeB4a276Fd201522621D and verified on Basescan.",
    "Task 11-B is not fully integrated on Base Sepolia: the live TavernRegistry at 0x7749473E36a8d6E741d9E581106E81CacAb7832a does not implement stakingContract()/setStakingContract(), so stakingContract could not be configured.",
    "Phase 2 redeploy superseded TavernRegistry 0x7749473E36a8d6E741d9E581106E81CacAb7832a, TavernEscrow 0x243fB879fBE521c5c227Da9EF731968413755131, and TavernStaking 0x50a8866F7E24441e636aFeB4a276Fd201522621D.",
